data.description: Welcome home!  This exquisite property offers the perfect blend of spaciousness, comfort and functionality.  Situated on a half acre lot, this home boasts an open floor plan, four bedrooms, an an abundance of living areas.  As you step inside, you will be greeted by a bright and inviting space.  The heart of the home is the kitchen, which serves as the central hub for entertaining.  Featuring stainless steel appliances, ample counter space, and a  center island.  Beyond the kitchen you will find four living areas and two dining areas.  The  livings spaces offers various option for relaxation, and entertainment.  Notably, one of the living areas boast its own private entrance, making it ideal for a pool house, a media room, or even a mother-in-law suite.  The master bedroom is very generous size,  with enough space for a sitting area.  One of the highlights of the outdoor living space where you will find a you oasis with a pool and captivating waterfall feature.
